@startuml
title 미핏 인터뷰 상태 머신

skinparam backgroundColor #FEFEFE
skinparam defaultFontSize 11
skinparam linetype ortho
skinparam state {
  BackgroundColor #E8F4FD
  BorderColor #2196F3
  ArrowColor #555555
  FontSize 11
  AttributeFontSize 10
  AttributeFontColor #455A64
}
skinparam state<<terminal>> {
  BackgroundColor #C8E6C9
  BorderColor #2E7D32
}
skinparam state<<errstate>> {
  BackgroundColor #FFCDD2
  BorderColor #C62828
}
skinparam state<<choice>> {
  BackgroundColor #FFF9C4
  BorderColor #FBC02D
}

[*] --> idle

state "idle" as idle
idle : 페이지 마운트 직후
idle : 세션/미디어 device 대기

state "ready" as ready
ready : 미디어 ready 완료
ready : Start 버튼 활성

state "starting" as starting
starting : startInterview API in-flight
starting : entry / startVideoAnalysis()
starting : entry / resetWarnings()

state "tts_playing" as tts
tts : 질문 TTS 재생 + 아바타 발화
tts : entry / resetText()
tts : entry / avatarSpeak(question)
tts : entry / playTtsText(question)
tts : entry / prepareRecording(turnId)

state "preparing_record" as prep
prep : TTS 종료 후 녹화 준비 완료 대기

state mode_choice <<choice>>

state "countdown" as cd
cd : 5~30초 랜덤 카운트다운 (real mode)
cd : entry / setTimeout(1s) -> COUNTDOWN_TICK

state "awaiting_start" as await_start
await_start : "말하기 시작" 클릭 대기 (practice mode)

state "speaking" as speak
speak : STT + 녹화 + 시선/고개 카운팅
speak : entry / startStt()
speak : entry / startTurnCounting()
speak : entry / startRecording(turnId)

state "submitting" as submit
submit : 답변 제출 + 백엔드 처리
submit : handler / stopStt()
submit : handler / stopTurnCounting()
submit : handler / stopRecording()
submit : handler / submitInterviewAnswer(...)

state "finished" as finished <<terminal>>
finished : 면접 완료
finished : entry / cleanup all media+stt+tts
finished : entry / navigate("/interview/results")

state "error" as error <<errstate>>
error : 복구 불가능한 오류

idle --> ready : MEDIA_READY
idle --> tts : RESUME(turnId, question)

ready --> starting : START
starting --> tts : QUESTION_ARRIVED
tts --> prep : TTS_DONE
prep --> mode_choice : RECORDING_READY

mode_choice --> cd : [isRealMode]
mode_choice --> await_start : [!isRealMode]

cd --> cd : COUNTDOWN_TICK\n[next > 0]
cd --> speak : COUNTDOWN_TICK\n[next <= 0]

await_start --> speak : PRACTICE_START
speak --> submit : SUBMIT
submit --> tts : ANSWER_ACCEPTED
submit --> finished : FINISH

finished --> [*]
error --> [*]

note bottom
  ★ 일시중지(Pause/Resume)는 이 머신과 **orthogonal** 합니다 ★
  • Zustand store `useInterviewSessionStore.isPaused` 에서 별도 관리 (Machine B)
  • speaking / tts_playing / submitting 등 어떤 상태에서도 paused 활성 가능
  • 녹화(MediaRecorder)는 paused 시 MediaRecorder.pause() 로 함께 중단되고,
    resume 시 MediaRecorder.resume() 으로 같은 instance 에서 이어서 녹화됨 (FR-INT-17~19)
  • 자세한 매트릭스 + 설계 의도: state-interview-machine.md
  • 시각화: state-interview-pause-resume.puml (Machine B 직교 머신)
end note

footer MeFit 코드 기반 State Diagram - frontend reducer machine (Machine A)
@enduml
